data.meta_description: Doh - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document lists contact information for the Department of Health in the Philippines, including names, titles, and contact details of key officials such as the Secretary, Undersecretaries, and Assistant Secretaries. It also lists the bureaus, centers, attached agencies, and special hospitals that fall under the Department of Health.
